The '''Lido Deck''' was one of many aboard the [[M-class|''M''-class]] [[Luxury liner/Legends|luxury liner]] [[Kuari Princess/Legends|''Kuari Princess'']]. Six [[swimming pool]]s were situated on this deck, including a competition-sized [[Ammonia/Legends|NH<sub>3</sub>]]/[[Mercury/Legends|Hg]] tank.<ref name="RPG">[[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game (first edition)|''Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game'']]</ref> The Observation Deck was situated on Lido Deck. Passengers watched the entry in to [[Maelstrom Nebula/Legends|the Maelstrom]] between [[Mantooine/Legends|Mantooine]] and [[Endoraan]].<ref name="RM">[[Riders of the Maelstrom (adventure)|''Riders of the Maelstrom'']]</ref>

